Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.52,0:22:33.05,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}extended its roots
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:40.91,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and put out a fruit that was still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.91,0:22:44.07,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.61,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:48.69,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.98,0:22:52.43,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The ideals and dreams just swell{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.43,0:22:55.34,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\fnGill Sans Std ExtraBold Display\b1\c&HBDCACF&}H{\r}ey, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.83,0:22:57.82,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.82,0:22:59.28,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:02.53,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}but it was so sour I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.53,0:23:06.00,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I couldn’t leave it behind like I have been
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.00,0:23:08.58,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.58,0:23:14.70,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.42,0:23:21.84,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I love it.
