Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.46,0:00:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so clumsy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.37,0:00:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just whine, help me pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can someone please help me pick these up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.37,0:00:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, they're everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.54,0:00:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's this tiny idiot's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.13,0:00:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's wrong, Aisaka-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga really loves Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks she has to be good because Santa is always watching her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All girls love Christmas, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.37,0:00:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two finding time to study for your exams with all these party preparations?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we've been studying as a group recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.91,0:01:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Aisaka-san always has good grades,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and your grades are always good too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Haruta-kun, Haruta-kun, and Haruta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haruta?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.71,0:01:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Haruta-kun too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.57,0:01:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun hasn't been helping with the preparations, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.54,0:01:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura ordered him to stay out of this so he could study.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.14,0:01:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me you two won't let your grades drop, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that you two might be\Nspending too much time on the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.07,0:01:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.52,0:01:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, are you coming to the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.41,0:01:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any dates on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the sake of my pride, I won't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.01,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really hope it's a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.90,0:01:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are putting a lot of effort into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll definitely reap the rewards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.57,0:03:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo! Taiga-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Minorin! Club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.42,0:03:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We spent the whole time working out in the gym!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda, hurry up or the coach will start complaining again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we really haven't been talking much lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.10,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.75,0:03:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party will definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.48,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin is being really weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll definitely cheer up if she comes to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to do our best to make it an amazing party!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.43,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you two doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got held up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in charge of the ornaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.89,0:04:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go redo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, should you really be saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you trying to be good for Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that for the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.12,0:05:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.26,0:05:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The P.E. teacher asked us to clean out the\Nstoreroom in return for letting us use the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let me take care of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura, make the stars with Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here are the scissors and glue.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.93,0:05:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold scissors like that, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold them like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my, they sure are getting along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go and help out over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.95,0:05:35.53,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, what are they trying to stir up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.16,0:05:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stir what up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb, you know I'm talking about Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...uh... liking Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:58.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately, it seems like everyone is trying to pair them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really obsessed with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.41,0:06:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I be jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.57,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...get pissed off when outsiders spread stuff about someone else's love life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how a father feels when his daughter is about to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.28,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I've never met my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not allowing her to fall, get hurt, or cry."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Watching the most precious woman of your life get taken away from you by another man."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.51,0:06:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not knowing if that man will treasure her as much as you do."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never had those thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely it won't be fun for you to\Nwatch Yuusaku and Taiga date, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the total opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.12,0:07:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not her father, but you treasure the\Nwoman you're determined not to lay a hand on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already have another woman in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like playing house. You three know exactly which characters you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like pretending to be daddy, mummy, and the baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to pretend to be daddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your relationship with Taiga seems really unnatural.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should stop playing this childish game of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been making mistakes all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.21,0:07:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wake up before you get hurt even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should forget everything and just start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you could also give me another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.82,0:07:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.21,0:07:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend you didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.75,0:07:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I even talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.56,0:08:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just forget everything I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, what you really don't understand is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, put your pencils down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It's over! It's finally over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:33.53,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.01,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet down and listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.01,0:08:37.52,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas! Christmas is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.52,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's normal school tomorrow and the day after,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.12,0:08:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so don't get too excited about Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to have lunch with Ryuuji and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.58,0:08:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have to go to practise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sadly, Minorin has club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I heard her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:09:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for turning you guys down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, it's nothing really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just seems like we haven't had a chance to talk lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.49,0:09:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, Taiga and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.18,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, our coach was taken over by the\Ndark side, so now our practice is harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.49,0:09:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She ran away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to create a chance for you guys to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.27,0:09:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we had left and arrived at the shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've said, "Sorry, I have something to do!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.81,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even planned a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Taiga sure is passionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.08,0:09:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There {\i1}will{\i0} be another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat something before we go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.17,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't going to lie, I really have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After I go home to get something, I need to go to the post office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, you don't need{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you free right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to have a talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come and have lunch with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay? Okay? Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Sorry, I have something to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.10,0:10:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the post office with her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ryuuji! I said you didn't need to come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.16,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what's with that gal girl pretending to be Kitamura's childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, scratch that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant, the honest girl, Kihara-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, it won't be a lie if I go to the post office with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The thing you need to get...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you plan to take them all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.76,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are none of your concern! Just help me get the cart!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wai{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it weren't Christmas, I would've beaten you up already,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the sake of being good, I'll forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Christmas presents for {\i1}that{\i0} family.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're planning to give them another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.60,0:11:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because of that, it's because it's Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because they're my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.93,0:11:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also got presents for you and Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you want to say, but I don't want to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get the cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.71,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa Claus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to an all-girls Catholic school since primary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was rejected by the high school because of bad behaviour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that school, you have to do volunteer work with the sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.13,0:12:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to put it this way, but we played with orphans and did some other odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The present with "Santa" written on it is actually for those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, presents for {\i1}that{\i0} family, and now for orphans?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I don't understand you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to tell them that there are\Npeople who are watching over them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas is a chance to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.19,0:12:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Even if you don't have parents and don't believe in God...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that's the case, there's someone watching over you."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want to show them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them to know that someone cares about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.15,0:12:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, it's self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's because I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...someone is actually watching over me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, that person is Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa, Santa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really believe in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.01,0:13:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly love Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The streets, shops... Everywhere is glittering.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s dazzling and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.82,0:13:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone looks really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is overflowing with happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm part of that happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be part of the happy, glittering scene on Christmas Eve,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.99,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while wearing a happy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really met Santa before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.36,0:13:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was when I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was on a Christmas Eve when my parents were still together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sleeping under the Christmas tree in the living room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.16,0:14:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up because it was cold,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I looked out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Santa was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He gave me a present and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.99,0:14:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"If you be a good child, I'll definitely come again."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it might have been a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, it was a really happy dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I'm stupid for believing in a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever, it's not like its real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I'm clinging to something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.13,0:14:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Christmas tree is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.95,0:15:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be really awesome once we put it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the party will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.91,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuri-chan, are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm not going for the sake of my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.86,0:15:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I should buy a present for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.92,0:15:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watches, bags, or even accessories!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a reward for thirty years of hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.61,0:15:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking that I'm wasting money, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.17,0:15:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking that I'm just a single woman who's falling for advertising tactics, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:28.42,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't waste money because I need seventy million yen for retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what if I stop myself from buying things,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.01,0:15:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then I can finally say, "Yay! I have a hundred million yen",
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.71,0:15:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before I know it, inflation in Japan gets so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.77,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that all the money I've saved becomes useless{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, huh?! I just predicted the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should buy myself an apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here! It's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Check if we have all the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you managed to get something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a decoration in a model show I was on, so I asked them if I could have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.96,0:15:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't I amazing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're a Stupid Chi', but you're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best tree ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.88,0:16:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one could disagree!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be even better once we put it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come on, let's get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the supporting parts all right like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.06,0:16:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! I'm excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the top part.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka-san, you look pretty light,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so can you get on my back and put this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the shoes I just went to the toilet with?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Different people really do have different interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.87,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, please take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.63,0:16:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you dozing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.36,0:16:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I think this is next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what was that for?! It was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.54,0:16:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your reflexes are pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.24,0:16:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from the Palmtop Tiger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's because I believe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...someone is actually watching over me somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you didn't actually have someone\Nwatching over you for the past seventeen years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.15,0:17:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.28,0:17:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have Kitamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also have Yasuko, Inko-chan, and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.37,0:17:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, Kushieda will definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll definitely reap the rewards!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we'll be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone will be happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone will be rewarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.40,0:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.90,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this from my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put it on the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.89,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful... Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.20,0:17:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, it looks really expensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although this is my favourite decoration,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't put it on my own Christmas tree because it was too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it on carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackout curtains are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The power source is okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,80)}All right, turn off the lights now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.23,0:18:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.33,0:18:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one got hurt, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an accident, it couldn't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.31,0:19:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, you're not at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just an unfortunate accident{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it was because I spaced out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost control of the ball, and it broke something very important to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I might not be able to fix it, just let me do whatever I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let Ryuuji hel{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop! Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.69,0:20:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me do this by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.05,0:20:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you help me, I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.09,0:20:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not helping you, I'm just doing what I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun... Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.15,0:20:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, isn't it beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's broken, it can be fixed,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.87,0:21:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.22,0:21:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't return it to the way it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's still shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.83,0:21:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know if I can fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.54,0:21:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, it can be fixed no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we're really...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.10,0:21:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cuter than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.95,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kushieda!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.85,0:21:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to come to the party tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.75,0:21:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll definitely be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.09,0:21:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go after all the trouble I've caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.38,0:21:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wait,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:22:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because I won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.97,0:22:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.59,0:22:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.75,0:23:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy night! Holy night! Holy night! Holy night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.71,0:23:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! It's a party on the holy night!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.13,0:23:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want more fruit punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Taiga?
